{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Martin Bokša Blog","author":"Martin Bokša"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"9d8df735-5f25-5890-8361-c36d827cb7b3","excerpt":"Za posledný môj rok som sa stretol s množstvom knižníc, ktoré sa týkajú Reactu.\nJe to dané najmä tým, že som nemal veľké predchádzajúce skúsenosti s Reactom\na…","html":"<p>Za posledný môj rok som sa stretol s množstvom knižníc, ktoré sa týkajú Reactu.\nJe to dané najmä tým, že som nemal veľké predchádzajúce skúsenosti s Reactom\na zároveň javascript je tak rýchly jazyk, že vychádzá v ňom každý deň\nnové množstvo knižníc.\nRád by som si tu odložil skúsenosti s nimi a priblížil vám čo všetko považujem\ndnes za nevynutné vedieť pri práci s Reactom.</p>\n<h2>Boilerplate</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/facebook/create-react-app\">create-react-app</a>\nak nemáte skúsenosti s Reactom, táto knižnica vám vytvorí boilerplate (alebo kostru) pre vašu\naplikáciu. Obsahuje všetky nevyhnuté konfigurácie a závislosti aby ste mohli\nrovno písať React a nemuseli sa o nič starať.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"no-text\"><pre class=\"language-no-text\"><code class=\"language-no-text\">What&#39;s included? React, JSX, ES6, TypeScript and Flow syntax support.</code></pre></div>\n<h2>Data Store</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/reduxjs/react-redux\">Redux</a> ide o globálny obchod s premennými. Je vhodný k tomu,\naby ste nemuseli preposielať premennú cez ďalších <em>x</em> komponent do hĺbky. Tak ju\nnapojíte na globálne obchod. Použitie napríklad: user data, aktuálna téma, stav aplikácie, …\nPoužíva sa často.</p>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/f4d335a45bb8c40a64b8333f4b6fb762/5f59d/redux.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 590px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 38.24091778202677%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"Redux\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/f4d335a45bb8c40a64b8333f4b6fb762/fb8a0/redux.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/f4d335a45bb8c40a64b8333f4b6fb762/1a291/redux.png 148w,\n/static/f4d335a45bb8c40a64b8333f4b6fb762/2bc4a/redux.png 295w,\n/static/f4d335a45bb8c40a64b8333f4b6fb762/fb8a0/redux.png 590w,\n/static/f4d335a45bb8c40a64b8333f4b6fb762/526de/redux.png 885w,\n/static/f4d335a45bb8c40a64b8333f4b6fb762/fa2eb/redux.png 1180w,\n/static/f4d335a45bb8c40a64b8333f4b6fb762/5f59d/redux.png 1569w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://reactjs.org/docs/context.html\">React Context</a> je to pomerne nová feature od Reactu.\nJe teoretickým nahraditeľom Reduxu. Tu sa, ale vytvorí <code class=\"language-text\">provider</code> dát a\njeho vnútorné komponenty vo vnútri ich vedia čitať pomocou <code class=\"language-text\">consumera</code>.</p>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/8aa95b679d0d05f86a8e16eea76e6a63/c312a/react-context.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 590px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 70.42253521126761%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"React Context\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/8aa95b679d0d05f86a8e16eea76e6a63/fb8a0/react-context.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/8aa95b679d0d05f86a8e16eea76e6a63/1a291/react-context.png 148w,\n/static/8aa95b679d0d05f86a8e16eea76e6a63/2bc4a/react-context.png 295w,\n/static/8aa95b679d0d05f86a8e16eea76e6a63/fb8a0/react-context.png 590w,\n/static/8aa95b679d0d05f86a8e16eea76e6a63/c312a/react-context.png 710w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/mobxjs/mobx\">MobX</a> ďalšia možnosť k uskladneniu\nglobálnych dát.</p>\n<h2>CSS</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/styled-components/styled-components\">Styled Component</a></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> Button <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> styled<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>a<span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token string\">`\n  /* This renders the buttons above... Edit me! */\n  display: inline-block;\n  border-radius: 3px;\n  padding: 0.5rem 0;\n  color: pink;\n`</span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token function\">render</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n    <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>Button\n      href<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"https://github.com/styled-components/styled-components\"</span>\n      target<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"_blank\"</span>\n    <span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n      GitHub\n    <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>Button<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token string\">``</span></span>\n\nMaterial <span class=\"token constant\">UI</span>\nhttps<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>github<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>com<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>mui<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>org<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>material<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>ui\n\nclassnames\nhttps<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>github<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>com<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>JedWatson<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>classnames\n\nreact<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>responsive\nhttps<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>github<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>com<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>contra<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>react<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>responsive\n\nReact DnD\nhttps<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>github<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>com<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>react<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>dnd<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>react<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>dnd\n\nReact Spring\nhttps<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>github<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>com<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>react<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>spring<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>react<span class=\"token operator\">-<